room_title: Escape room "Once Upon a Crime" by Mission Escape Rooms in Annapolis
room_description: You and your team are members of an elite fairytale crime unit known as FABLE (also known as The Office of Fairytale Assistance Business & Law Enforcement). As agents of FABLE, it is your duty to serve and protect the Fairytale Realm, investigating crimes and pursuing magic and non-magic offenders, alike. A recent spike in criminal activity across the Realm has your team working overtime, but you just got a break in the case. One of your field agents just sent you a coded message that could be critical to solving the case!
